translations.MARKET_INFO_DESC_EXGO:
X Goals is a market that settles the outcome of a game based on a team's statistical performance instead of goals.


We assign a goal value to Corners, Shots on Target and Cards, and the 'winner' is the team with the highest score.


Values are as follows:


  • Shot on Target = 0.2 of a goal
  • Corner = 0.15 of a goal
  • Yellow Card = -0.1 of a goal
  • Red Card = -0.25 of a goal
